const Colors = {
    primary: '#1D4123',
    secondary: '#639d04',

    lightGreen: '#D8F9C9',
    lightGray: '#D2D9D3',

    orange: '#FC8004',
    blue: '#3365AC',
    green: '#2DA440',
    red: '#8E1B1B',
    yellow: '#FFC107',

    white: '#FFFFFF',
    dark: '#000',
    grey: '#ADADAD'
};

export default Colors;
